# Security Policy

## Reporting a Vulnerability
Please email security@royalmixglobal.com (PGP key) or open a private GitHub Security Advisory.

## Supported versions
This repo follows semantic versioning. For critical issues contact us immediately.

## Responsible disclosure
We request 90 days to respond and remediate before public disclosure.

## Secrets
Do NOT commit secrets. Use GitHub Secrets / AWS Secrets Manager.
